{"tid":246552,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 條女真係好撚正呀...","createTime":"2017-05-17T06:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T08:45:30.000Z","uid":4806,"like":42,"dislike":210,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58cdb246fc50a96f6405ff9b1e6cdd9bb203f3d5","tid":246552,"uid":4806,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/17/141710_2e8256d9f7a418aab60a6d2e6254567a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2F141710_2e8256d9f7a418aab60a6d2e6254567a.jpg&h=804073c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條女真係好撚索呀!!!  好想廝開佢條裙，一手扯撚爛佢條底褲 !!!  一口吸落去佢隻美鮑仔度係咁吸啜!!!  條利伸到最盡把佢陰道內所有蜜汁同閪屎全部奶乾淨!!!  連佢閪邊o的油都要奶埋!!!  兩隻手大大吸手狂搾佢對大波,食指同中指用70%力夾佢奶頭!!!  再轉身放條巨撚入佢個口度!!!頂佢吊鐘!!望住佢流眼淚個樣時，  再轉身用100%力度一野屌落佢個淫閪度!!!  之後插完屎窿!!!!再插佢個口迫佢食返自己o的屎!!!  屌緊佢個口時,用三條手指插入佢個閪度係咁了!!!  最後插到個閪最盡射精!!一定要搞大佢個肚!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcf424c39b8ad1c5835f6b50afb3cb01e548935","tid":246552,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"普通<br />\ncsk_alison 正d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9680a16b7f291ca2a797fd9bf3cd5fc59e26c159","tid":246552,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通<br />\ncsk_alison 正d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCsk alison無波無籮